Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:52.84,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}ただ君といると
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:56.99,OPJ,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}夢見た世界が
