Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.86,0:00:02.60,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}独自一人
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.92,0:00:08.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}迷失在旅途之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.16,0:00:17.26,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}彷徨之心始终居无归处
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.54,0:00:21.71,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}然而现今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.27,0:00:25.56,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}却阔步迈向远方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.86,0:00:30.01,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}于是与你在路上
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.57,0:00:34.19,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}相会了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.95,0:00:38.63,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}旅者们放声歌唱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.08,0:00:42.06,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}虽然是未曾听闻
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.66,0:00:46.98,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}却感到无限怀念
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.20,0:00:52.84,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}只因你在我身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.14,0:00:56.99,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}梦里见到的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.23,0:01:01.16,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}究竟在何处
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.43,0:01:05.46,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}快去寻找它吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.70,0:01:09.64,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}就在风的彼岸
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.88,0:01:13.74,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\be1}在冰封的黎明
